  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV58">
<l>kaḻaṟala moṉṟē nilamuḻu tāyiṟ ṟorukaḻalpōy</l>
<l>niḻaṟara vellā vicumpu niṟaintatu nīṇṭavaṇṭat</l>
<l>tuḻaṟalar ñāṉac cuṭarviḷak kāyuyarn tōraiyillā</l>
<l>vaḻaṟalar tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉeṉ ṉōviṅ kaḷakkiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One sole of [his] ankleted [foot] leapt over the whole ground. One ankleted [foot] went</l>
<l>[and] filled all the sky so as to give shade. In the vast space,</l>
<l>as a roaming flower, a glowing lamp of knowledge, without anyone higher,</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ with mud-blooming lotus [eyes], what will he measure here?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
